POSX Framework v1.0.0
Production Baseline - RLS + Security Hardened

Release Date: 2025-11-07
Status: Production Ready ✅
Code Name: Foundation

Core Features:
- Row Level Security (RLS) with FORCE enforcement
- Production CSP (no unsafe-inline)
- CSRF Smart Exemption for API
- Health Checks with proper error handling
- Multi-site isolation
- Admin cross-site read-only access

Security Checklist:
✅ RLS with atomic=False migrations
✅ CSP without unsafe-inline
✅ CSRF exemption middleware
✅ Proper WSGI/ASGI setup
✅ Static files handling
✅ Robust health checks
